MALACAÑANG Manila

PROCLAMATION NO. 877

RESERVING FOR MARKET SITE PURPOSES CERTAIN PARCELS OF LAND OF THE PUBLIC DOMAIN SITUATED IN THE MUNICIPALITY OF TUMAUINI, PROVINCE OF ISABELA, ISLAND OF LUZON

Upon recommendation of the Secretary of Environment and Natural Resources, and by virtue of the powers vested in me by law, I, CORAZON C. AQUINO, President of the Philippines, do hereby withdraw from sale or settlement and reserve for market site purposes under the administration of the Municipality of Tumauini, Province of Isabela, subject to private rights, if any there be, certain parcels of land of the public domain containing an aggregate area of Twelve Thousand Seven Hundred Twenty Two (12,722) Square meters, situated in the Municipality of Tumauini, Province of Isabela, Island of Luzon and more particularly described as follows, to wit:

Lot 2235, Pls-946

A PARCEL OF LAND Lot No. 2235, Pls-946, as surveyed for Municipal Government of Tumauini, situated at the Barrio of San Pedro, Municipality of Tumauini, Province of Isabela, Island of Luzon. Bounded on the SW., along line 1-2 by National Road; on the NW., NE. and SE., along lines 2-3-4-5- 6-7-1 by Municipal Road. Beginning at a point marked “1” of Lot 2235, Pls-946 being N. 06 deg. 29′ E., 479.71 m. from BLLM No. 1 Pls-946, Tumauini Public Land Subdivision. Thence . . . .

