Lot 2237, Pls-964

A parcel of Land of Lot No. 2237, Pls-964, as surveyed for Municipal Government of Tumauini, Portion of Public Market, situated at the Barrio of San Pedro, Municipality of Tumauini, Province of Isabela, Island of Luzon. Bounded on the SE., along line 1-2 by Municipal Road; on the SW., along lines 2-3-4 by Lot 2238, Pls-964; on the NW., along line 4-5 by Lot 2252, Pls-964, along line 5-6 by lot 2258, Pls-964; on the NE., along line 6-1 by Municipal road. Beginning at a point marked “1” of Lot 2237, Pls- 964 being N. 09 deg. 29′ E., 623.60 m. from BLLM No. 1, Pls-964, Police Station, Tumauini, Public Land Subdivision. Thence . . . .

